      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DYNASTY REWARD (2) looks hard to beat. Working up to a win and freshened for this. Has the claim and inside draw and sure to go close. HIGHSTRUNG (4) is a consistent performer with two minor placings from three starts this campaign. Was prominent throughout and finished 2.75 lengths from the winner in third at the latest outing over 1400m at this track. Back and trip and looks hard to beat in this line-up. DENUTO (1) has not appeared since he finished seventh over 1000m at this track on November 1. Former NSW galloper yet to fire in three runs in the NT but will have derived benefit from the break. Can make his presence felt. ROSEBUD LASS (5) settled back on debut last time out and battled on evenly to finish fifth over 1100m at this track. Back to maiden class and should be much improved. Has upside and worth including. ARTISTIC FLAIR (3) has had one run this area and should be better.",
